{"tid":2324495,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"電影製作助理早前承認非法集結判囚3月 今放棄刑期上訴即時服刑","createTime":"2020-12-14T03:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T09:40:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6619932a4e43773f49ae9e8390de53aa85160216","tid":2324495,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12094&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725NXdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=3a3731e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12094</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第廿九庭<br />\n#李運騰法官<br />\n#不服刑罰上訴 <br />\n楊(23)<br />\n(#0811將軍澳 非法集結;於9月25日被判處監禁3個月，後申請保釋等候上訴獲批)<br />\n<br />\n被控於2019年8月11日在將軍澳佳景路 9 號浩明苑地下外參與非法集結<br />\n<br />\n上次求情<br />\n <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9812&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725NXdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=df15ab74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9812</a><br />\n法庭於12月14日收到放棄上訴通知書。被告就原先3個月刑期服刑。🛑"},{"pid":"51d72c3b47b4732d5f792dba6ea806f7b11ff4fa","tid":2324495,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:40:55.000Z","msg":"23歲電影製作助理去年8月11日，與近50人一起以雷射筆照射將軍澳警署，他早前承認一項非法集結罪，被判監禁3個月，並獲准保釋等候上訴。他原訂今在高等法院進行刑期上訴聆訊，但他向法庭申請放棄上訴，李運騰法官正式宣布其刑期上訴被撤銷，並需即時服刑。<br />\n<br />\n從事電影製作的23歲被告承認於去年8月11日，在將軍澳佳景路9號浩明苑地下外，參與非法集結。觀塘裁判法院主任裁判官徐綺薇在9月判刑時指，當時深夜12時有50多人聚集在將軍澳警署「燒衣紙」及叫囂，又用雷射筆照射警署，作出挑釁性行為。被告與其他人在警方發出警告後仍拒絕離開，繼續用雷射筆照向警署，導致一名警員眼部不適，故須判以阻嚇性刑罰，來確保維護公共秩序。"},{"pid":"5858ee04d2297546c7c44ca9fd5e83f40aa9cf78","tid":2324495,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:41:57.000Z","msg":"繼續用雷射筆照向警署<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁撚遠"},{"pid":"079882e457b380a1d3385c7dc78abf8ee18796bc","tid":2324495,"uid":160592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:42:59.000Z","msg":"係咪都就3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d238a46d60caf7df9be2e6a3032f26559a3ae271","tid":2324495,"uid":43062,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"吹撚到咁都襲到警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afe66a048313a128ddbb25399cc8e2d7acfffb7","tid":2324495,"uid":268519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:44:18.000Z","msg":"屌 3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb983eab4f077f20c72977161cc24e18aee7ba0","tid":2324495,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d238a46d60caf7df9be2e6a3032f26559a3ae271","tid":2324495,"uid":43062,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"吹撚到咁都襲到警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"從來無驗傷報告話曱甴有傷,純係曱甴話係,班狗官就照跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b166651bb1844507b40c2e8ebf88bc5d357e47d7","tid":2324495,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2afe66a048313a128ddbb25399cc8e2d7acfffb7","tid":2324495,"uid":268519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:44:18.000Z","msg":"屌 3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:58:18.000Z","msg":"上訴分分鐘判你半年以上"},{"pid":"8746ae72ba278b97b7321c663f4f0545a37439b9","tid":2324495,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgm