DRENRIJKCEYEEQC2LY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201214%2FRH3WXOWODRENRIJKCEYEEQC2LY%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725NXdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=e9b0ebee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201214%2FRH3WXOWODRENRIJKCEYEEQC2LY%2F&h=b040c35e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201214/RH3WXOWODRENRIJKCEYEEQC2LY/</a>"},{"pid":"397edb115ac7df4745b83dcda925aea9fd345942","tid":2324495,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6fbe43720630491e1e3366f26d179399241ea8","tid":2324495,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"而家閒閒地都10個月<br />\n律政司唔覆核刑期已經算執到"},{"pid":"60e22e99a1a4e23745b91ad7b6de24493b6f43da","tid":2324495,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}